{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-38","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 38","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Atribut elementa <code>action</code> pokazuje gde podaci forme treba da budu poslati.</p>\n<p>Ovo je primer elementa <code>form</code> sa svojstvom elementa <code>action</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;form action=\"/submit-url\">&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>\n<p>U ovom primeru, <code>action=\"/submit-url\"</code> kažem pretraživaču da podaci forme bi trebalo poslati na putanju <code>/submit-url</code>.</p>\n<p>Dodaj svojstvo elementa <code>action</code> sa vrednošću <code>https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo</code> na polje <code>form</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804d7","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-38"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[35,38],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>form</code> mora imati otvarajući i zatvarajući tag u ispravnom redosledu. Možda vam nedostaje jedan ili oba neophodna taga, ili ih imate u pogrešnom redosledu.</p>","testString":"const noSpaces = code.replace(/\\s/g, '');\nassert(\n  document.querySelector('form') &&\n    code.match(/<\\/form>/g) &&\n    noSpaces.indexOf('<form') < noSpaces.indexOf('</form>')\n);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>form</code>, koji je postavljen unutar elementa <code>section</code>, treba da bude ispod elementa <code>h2</code>. Imate element <code>h2</code> i element <code>form</code> u pogrešnom redosledu.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelector('form')?.previousElementSibling?.nodeName, 'H2');"},{"text":"<p>Element vašeg <code>form</code> ne bi trebalo da sadrži nikakav sadržaj. Uklonite sve komponente HTML ili tekst između oznaka elementa <code>form</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelector('form')?.innerHTML?.trim(), 0);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>form</code> nedostaje atribut elementa <code>action</code>. Uverite se da postoji razmak nakon imena otvarajuće oznake i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih imena atributa elemenata.</p>","testString":"const form = document.querySelector('form');\nassert(form.hasAttribute('action'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element od <code>form</code> mora imati svojstvo elementa <code>action</code> sa vrednošću <code>https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo</code>.</p>","testString":"const form = document.querySelector('form');\nassert(\n  form\n    .getAttribute('action')\n    .match(/^https:\\/\\/freecatphotoapp\\.com\\/submit-cat-photo$/)\n);"},{"text":"<p>Iako ste postavili atribut elementa <code>action</code> za URL tačno, savetuje se uvek da obuhvatite vrednost atributa elementa i navodnike.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  !/\\<form\\s+action\\s*=\\s*https:\\/\\/freecatphotoapp\\.com\\/submit-cat-photo/.test(\n    code\n  )\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-38","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-39","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-37","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804d7","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-38"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}